Ghostunnel wouldn't exist without the work of many others. Thanks to everyone
who has contributed code, reported bugs, or built the libraries we depend on.

## Origins

Ghostunnel was written by [Cedric Staub](https://github.com/csstaub) at
[Square](https://squareup.com) (now [Block](https://block.xyz)) in 2015.
Square open-sourced the project and supported its early development.

## Go's crypto/tls

Go's `crypto/tls` package does the heavy lifting. Ghostunnel is essentially
a thin layer on top of it. Without a TLS implementation this good in the
standard library, a project like Ghostunnel wouldn't make much sense.

## Forked & Incorporated Code

### certigo (Square/Block)

The `certloader` package incorporates certificate-decoding and keystore logic
originally from [certigo](https://github.com/square/certigo), Square's
certificate inspection tool. The following code was forked and adapted:

- `certloader/decode.go` -- certificate/key decoding helpers
- `certloader/jceks/` -- Java JCEKS keystore parser

Original copyright: Block, Inc. Licensed under the Apache License 2.0.

### certstore (Ben Toews)

The `certstore` package for platform-specific keychain access (macOS Keychain,
Windows Certificate Store) is derived from work by
[Ben Toews](https://github.com/mastahyeti). Licensed under the MIT License.

## Major Dependencies

| Dependency | Purpose |
|---|---|
| [kingpin](https://github.com/alecthomas/kingpin) | Command-line flag parsing |
| [certmagic](https://github.com/caddyserver/certmagic) | ACME / Let's Encrypt certificate management |
| [go-jose](https://github.com/go-jose/go-jose) | JOSE / JWE support |
| [go-spiffe](https://github.com/spiffe/go-spiffe) | SPIFFE Workload API integration |
| [pkcs11key](https://github.com/letsencrypt/pkcs11key) | PKCS#11 hardware security module support |
| [OPA](https://github.com/open-policy-agent/opa) | Open Policy Agent for declarative access control |
| [go-proxyproto](https://github.com/pires/go-proxyproto) | PROXY protocol v2 support |
| [go-pkcs12](https://pkg.go.dev/software.sslmate.com/src/go-pkcs12) | PKCS#12 keystore parsing |
| [smallstep/pkcs7](https://github.com/smallstep/pkcs7) | PKCS#7 certificate handling |
| [go-metrics](https://github.com/rcrowley/go-metrics) | Application metrics |
| [prometheus/client_golang](https://github.com/prometheus/client_golang) | Prometheus metrics export |
| [go-systemd](https://github.com/coreos/go-systemd) | systemd socket activation |
| [go-landlock](https://github.com/landlock-lsm/go-landlock) | Landlock sandboxing on Linux |
| [go_reuseport](https://github.com/kavu/go_reuseport) | SO_REUSEPORT socket support |
| [gRPC-Go](https://github.com/grpc/grpc-go) | gRPC transport for SPIFFE Workload API |

